INTERNATIONAL WORKSHOP ON ENTERPRISE KNOWLEDGE DEVELOPMENT    -   EKD '94



BILBAO - SPAIN,   HOTEL ERCILLA,   27 - 28 OCTOBER 1994



The first International Workshop on Enterprise Knowledge Development, to be
held in Bilbao on 27 and 28 October 1994, brings together leading experts
from industry, commerce and academia to address and debate key business
issues.
The focus is on the use of business models to develop adaptive business
solutions.


