DEMONSTRATORS   (16.00 - 18.00)

Practical application of  business models to develop adaptive business
solutions will be demonstrated.

     Formulation of marketing-mix for consultancy services
     Integrated Resource Management

The first demonstrator will show how a generic marketing model can be
instantiated in a specific company to support the formulation of the
marketing strategy for a number of services and vertical markets.

The second demonstrator will show how practical elements of resource
management  are linked to business processes and organisational design.  A
schedule for allocation of resources (people and technologies) to support a
new marketing strategy within specific constraints is derived.

Demonstrations will also be available throughout the workshop.



